
https://itexamanswers.net/4-4-1-1-packet-tracer-configuring-zone-based-policy-firewall-zpf-answers.html

Brief: you will create the zones, and add interfaces to them. After, a zone-pair is created establishing who is the source and who is the destination, and the policy (with the access control list) to be followed.

A interface can only be part of one zone.
